{"tid":84070,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"紫薯 haagen dazs","createTime":"2017-01-17T09:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T16:30:57.000Z","uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54bd6715ee06ab50dc8c45593a14af37b22f70b5","tid":84070,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20160719/photo/bkn-20160719182815653-0719_00982_001_01p.jpg?20160719182828\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20160719%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160719182815653-0719_00982_001_01p.jpg%3F20160719182828&h=d889d160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前係日本食過 好好味<br />\n返香港好似話711有入貨<br />\n不過好似賣晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴打知道邊仲有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b34ba0ba7991137ce88a065109a3ac90530722f","tid":84070,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:15:18.000Z","msg":"7－11"},{"pid":"299c33abec52b90c4e51cd35b7ad9ab8fadbd84b","tid":84070,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:24:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7－11</blockquote><br />\n俾間分店地址黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大約咩地方"},{"pid":"fa6dcf1c3c3f112231a29bdf5bfad7564d6c73bf","tid":84070,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>7－11</blockquote><br />\n俾間分店地址黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大約咩地方</blockquote><br />\n應該賣哂好耐啦<br />\n上個月頭同南瓜味係7仔一齊做限定架<br />\n月尾都已經唔見有"},{"pid":"61ff058916454e5bad8ab573134d5190c7475965","tid":84070,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:40:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>7－11</blockquote><br />\n俾間分店地址黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ton